{"tid":563281,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[石器時代私服] 星樂園【無掛 高清 無職業3.0版本 多種解析度選擇】","createTime":"2018-02-16T17:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T17:29:13.000Z","uid":12754,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b91b7e9bd12154eda1757e0801bc4038704333","tid":563281,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:48:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 星樂園 StongAge </span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">網址 : <a href=\"http://www.starsa.net/forum.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starsa.net%2Fforum.php&d=NuC2pLmyAj%2BpAB0WRKJ8Hv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=bb2af827\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.starsa.net/forum.php</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《基礎設置》</strong><br />\n~專為台、港、澳玩家設計~<br />\n經典回合制網路遊戲，輕鬆掛機不費力<br />\n無掛高清版本，多種解析度選擇，高規格體驗經典遊戲<br />\n<br />\n遊戲版本：3.0版+陸地融合寵<br />\n經驗倍率：平日10倍/假日12倍、合擊經驗值額外提升<br />\n多開限制：1台電腦限制雙開<br />\n人物最高等級：5轉140級 無職業<br />\n寵物最高等級：1轉140級<br />\n最高合成裝備：20級<br />\n當前開放莊園：薩姆吉爾、瑪麗娜絲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《星樂園特色》</strong><br />\nღ 新手加入，立即獲得新手騎寵，另外贈送新手套裝(免氣滋潤、免氣毒)。<br />\nღ 完成新手任務可獲得『新手成長禮包』，每1、3、5轉生還可再次領獎！<br />\nღ 三轉前智慧之果無限領取；三轉開始可每日簽到可獲得多項好禮！<br />\nღ 五轉領取轉生寵『帖拉所伊朵』，可向導師習得隨機1~6個「T 一級必殺 改」！<br />\nღ 不販售79滿石女寵、不出打臉寵！<br />\nღ 每晚皆有競技場積分活動，採隨機自動分隊機制。<br />\nღ 開放寵物回爐，愛寵不怕素質渣。<br />\nღ 超多元技能組、平衡1.82寵物素質、融合寵不能轉生<br />\nღ 開放多種造型皮膚隨意替換。<br />\nღ 大小地圖可任意切換！<br />\nღ 超強ESC系統，便利功能一應俱全。<br />\nღ 滑鼠滾輪可切換背包、聊天視窗卷軸。<br />\nღ 專業營運團隊、高品質服務、更新不間斷！<br />\n...<br />\n更多遊戲特色等你來體驗，快來加入『星樂園』！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《遊戲內容展示》</strong><br />\n 任務進度查詢，任務不漏接！<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.starsa.net/data/attachment/forum/201801/29/223707n5tvsjvdxjqp0zz4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starsa.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201801%2F29%2F223707n5tvsjvdxjqp0zz4.png&h=c7b9a024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 地圖可任務切換大小，解任務、跑圖更便利！<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n 星樂園商城僅提供一般消耗品，不販售Lv79滿石女寵、不出打臉寵！<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 每日簽到就送來吉卡，獎品多，還要更多！<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.starsa.net/data/attachment/forum/201801/29/223721gwnp0zhrpz6lh39a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starsa.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201801%2F29%2F223721gwnp0zhrpz6lh39a.png&h=8f2505a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 競技場積分活動，玩家互動滿分！<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n 訪問擺攤商品可立即反映現有的貨幣類型，不用花冤枉錢！<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n 寵物排行榜，愛寵素質大比拚！<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.starsa.net/data/attachment/forum/201801/29/223717vply71ad2slsgfda.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starsa.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201801%2F29%2F223717vply71ad2slsgfda.png&h=fe9b0d85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 造型屋NPC，外觀造型再加分，持續新增中！<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.starsa.net/data/attachment/forum/201801/29/223714qwjsse8mzxcqlezg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starsa.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201801%2F29%2F223714qwjsse8mzxcqlezg.png&h=328ba01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 野外抓寵可獲得特殊技能(欲觀看完整技能請加入社團討論區)！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.starsa.net/data/attachment/forum/201801/30/013710cuccup2yu4upqn2u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starsa.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201801%2F30%2F013710cuccup2yu4upqn2u.png&h=ae6e73c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43361946ebb0b8a90bd2cd016ceb969fa7b85885","tid":563281,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T18:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd21b89b634dfab9c3f4871838ff4201cb7feed6","tid":563281,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T18:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c6bf2bc2718c048e67abe2bc29bc3bb81eef18","tid":